---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Me | The Musings of Matt Domko">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none about-prose">
        <h1>About Me</h1>
        <p>Learn more about my background, expertise, and professional journey.</p>

        <h2>Professional Summary</h2>
        <p>
          I started my career in the US Army, starting as a Systems Engineer, promoted to Engineering
          Manager, and then later selected to help form the Cyber Protection Brigade as a Security
          Engineer. Those first 10 years of my career taught me a lot about leadership, project
          management, and how to build a team that succeeds in a resource constrained environment.
        </p>
        <p>
          Since then, I&rsquo;ve had the opportunity to dive deep into software and security
          engineering challenges at tech companies like Facebook and Amazon, and apply the things I
          learned there at smaller companies that need both technical skills and thoughtful leaders.
        </p>

        <h2>Why do I get out of bed?</h2>
        <p>
          &ldquo;Bosses&rdquo; and &ldquo;Managers&rdquo; are a dime a dozen. The world needs more
          Leaders. My favorite memory about every role I&rsquo;ve ever had is the moment that things
          &ldquo;clicked&rdquo; for the team&hellip;
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>They have someone to support them.</li>
          <li>
            They are on a team where our shared belief is &ldquo;if you take care of the people, the
            people will take care of the business&rdquo;.
          </li>
          <li>
            The team we built together is the best team they&rsquo;ve ever been on, and they will
            strive to take our values with them wherever they work.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Areas of Expertise</h2>
        <h3>Leadership</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Strategic Planning</li>
          <li>Team Development</li>
          <li>Change Management</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Security</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Cloud and Application Security</li>
          <li>Detection and Response</li>
          <li>Security Architecture</li>
          <li>Compliance Frameworks</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Technology</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Cloud Infrastructure</li>
          <li>DevOps Practices</li>
          <li>System Integration</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-prose :global(h2) {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }
  .about-prose :global(h3) {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .about-prose :global(h3 + p) {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
</style>
